Class VRTFormatOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gvsig.raster.tools.app.basic.tool.raw.tool.VRTFormatOptions

  • public class VRTFormatOptions
extends Object
    This class contains some information to manage the VRT file formats. It has the possible values for the params.
